 It's totally open and freely expressed and just no boundaries.

00:09:06.000 --> 00:09:11.000
 In another way, it's almost like it's the most pervasive.

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:14.000
 It includes the outer and the inner.

00:09:14.000 --> 00:09:18.000
 In a way, it's almost like, "Oh, it's more obvious because it's so pervasive."

00:09:18.000 --> 00:09:26.000
 But it's more subtle, it's more the most, maybe the most inner.

