 Most of the source.

00:09:30.000 --> 00:09:41.000
 I had an answer from my own practice about the thoughts on the three types of compassion.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:51.000
 I started out and I didn't really connect that much with the Four Noble Truths.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:56.000
 They didn't seem very profound to me.

