 So then it leads into understanding how we see things

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:43.000
 and then when we see that when we really understand what causes the suffering,

00:10:43.000 --> 00:10:50.000
 then we could more easily see that it is not the way that things are

00:10:50.000 --> 00:10:56.000
 or our perceptions that are causing suffering are not the way things actually are.

00:10:56.000 --> 00:11:03.000
 So then that could lead to emptiness.

00:11:03.000 --> 00:11:09.000
 And that's part of what like Rinpoche say, I think, in that next paragraph.

