 It's actually the cause of samsara is our holding.

00:36:15.000 --> 00:36:22.000
 And when we actually loosen up and get more flexible, what happens is we become more inclusive.

00:36:22.000 --> 00:36:29.000
 Our sphere of being sensitive to others, being sensitive to ourselves gets more flexible.

00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:34.000
 We become more sensitive. We're not holding so tightly in a specific way.

00:36:34.000 --> 00:36:41.000
 We're functioning in a much more varied, inclusive, complex, fully functional way.

