 But then it's a good point to say that we can do it either way, depending on our style.

00:40:04.000 --> 00:40:08.000
 If compassion comes more naturally, that will lead to become more inclusive

00:40:08.000 --> 00:40:10.000
 and to see things more clearly, emptiness nature.

00:40:10.000 --> 00:40:15.000
 If emptiness or the absolute realization comes more easily for different people,

00:40:15.000 --> 00:40:17.000
 then it should open our heart.

00:40:17.000 --> 00:40:21.000
 And if the one doesn't lead to the other, then something's off in the practice.

00:40:21.000 --> 00:40:24.000
 And that's the path, because something's constantly off.

00:40:24.000 --> 00:40:27.000
 Otherwise we'd be on all the time. We'd be bodhisattvas.

00:40:27.000 --> 00:40:31.000
 But so it's beautiful that it works either way.

00:40:31.000 --> 00:40:34.000
 Nature's so accommodating.

00:40:34.000 --> 00:40:39.000
 And that works with individual people's own personality types too.

